{"tid":23687,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美AIT前處長司徒文：美國從來都沒講過中國擁有台灣主權","createTime":"2016-12-05T05:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T06:39:27.000Z","uid":35790,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93a10a4dc08af40b2df0b3862154b95725147878","tid":23687,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:53:04.000Z","msg":"司徒文：美國過去「一個中國」政策是錯的<br />\n<br />\n2016-12-05 11:35<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國準總統川普與我國總統蔡英文在電話中討論台美事務，引起全球關注，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">美國在台協會（AIT）台北辦事處前處長司徒文（William Stanton）對此表示，美國過去「一個中國」的政策是錯的，而且他強調美國從來都沒講過中國擁有台灣的主權。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n由媒體人周玉蔻主持的《蔻蔻早餐》廣播節目，今日以電話連線訪問了司徒文，訪問他對於川蔡熱線的看法。司徒文首先表示，這應該是川普幕僚作出的計畫與建議，而不是台灣單方面的行動，他認為這是一個很正面的事情，也強調美國早就該做了。<br />\n<br />\n司徒文還說「一個中國」的政策是有問題的，美國方面從未講過中國對台灣擁有主權。司徒文最後提醒，這個溝通的管道既然達成了，那麼可以繼續努力維持並提升，畢竟這是過去馬政府想要做卻沒做到的事情。<br />\n(自由時報)"},{"pid":"32ff50c766a9620e4f39a6835ed9fe6c94eb7800","tid":23687,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T05:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88239eff88a4b56ac3f96112f474d84850d1be1f","tid":23687,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T06:06:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a61b146a5f35f1f25c72666f06831820366974c","tid":23687,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T06:08:23.000Z","msg":"in 侵，我信"},{"pid":"d39196d80d91970a091bc0d4bbfd57284adb7a45","tid":23687,"uid":22080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T06:15:42.000Z","msg":"侵侵好波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cdcca4bb24e215d9ca147a72ea7694d61d359fa","tid":23687,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T06:25:17.000Z","msg":"三個建交公報已經癈癈地"},{"pid":"8740c86a154f3d68674ffb4ce5f164685560ab78","tid":23687,"uid":41853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T09:59:30.000Z","msg":"但一樣從來無承認過台灣係主權國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cf078133a4d97cb8e951060176e560acb949e4b","tid":23687,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:02:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但一樣從來無承認過台灣係主權國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依台灣綠營說法<br />\n根據舊金山和約<br />\n台灣主權係由美國暫時托管"},{"pid":"2d00321f5d9c7e4e44ea8c25c9a3fe64b17fa672","tid":23687,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:03:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但一樣從來無承認過台灣係主權國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有d野係做得唔講得<br />\n台灣去美國免簽已經係承認左台灣主權獨立"},{"pid":"d0a24b57199ef87e367fabbf62554e0241b4839e","tid":23687,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2388c364f914ad7e82f470d8f54aa53b433f425","tid":23687,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:23:10.000Z","msg":"一個中國<br />\n一個台灣<br />\n<br />\n冇錯啊"},{"pid":"cd77b836e1e8337af893f7712f5f18e13deb7e4e","tid":23687,"uid":7632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:48:44.000Z","msg":"一個中国<br />\n一個台灣<br />\n一個香港<br />\n<br />\n都冇錯啊"},{"pid":"0c87fd94bb991bf0e64f037ed51eebe7539e4413","tid":23687,"uid":7632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qsh4c65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqsh4c65.jpg&h=39db8ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港喺美國眼中係國家"},{"pid":"0e0255652dcef8d68145acc0f39ce9d4dd956ede","tid":23687,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T02:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c490c17f44b03c3551eb4af35799eda6bde2996","tid":23687,"uid":3698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T03:34:19.000Z","msg":"川菜熱線...<br />\n打電話問水煮牛肉點整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08e509c8c7163675e8a60d8647c4a3e89a58a68","tid":23687,"uid":25350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T03:47:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197dda74fdd0f62db8df245d00e750c691c4b0ac","tid":23687,"uid":43597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T03:49:22.000Z","msg":"一中一台 無錯呀"},{"pid":"5305c8981581f314810a80b10f4ec355469fef13","tid":23687,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T05:52:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20996be56d1be8a22e98a4f7c68bcd53f61ebccd","tid":23687,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:25:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qsh4c65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqsh4c65.jpg&h=39db8ffb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港喺美國眼中係國家</blockquote><br />\n香港做到country，係中國默許援予既主權，因為中國比，所以先可以以country名義出現。所以用呢點黎打飛機冇咩意義，因為d A片都係中國比你。<br />\n<br />\n同台灣唔同，台灣個country地位係比中國壓制左，因為中國唔比，所以大部分國家都唔承認。如果有人比台灣以country身份出現，咁就值得打飛機，因為代表左果個國家defy緊中國，好似美國呢個case咁"},{"pid":"e32e025c9b8d6325ad80821e9a4fb4007a670d9b","tid":23687,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:39:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但一樣從來無承認過台灣係主權國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有d野係做得唔講得<br />\n台灣